Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:08.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}融掉的棒冰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:13.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}回溯的记忆
