Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.17,0:01:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难得那么早干完活的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不挑食才能茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚脐要被抢走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被住在三町目的大叔抢走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那样欠妥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不敢苟同你一味只是表扬的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是孩子得意忘形从此不再努力怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  孩子可是很敏锐的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到表扬之后为了与之相称
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们反而会自己做出努力以期改变的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法太过乐观了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些讨论就留在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭前快把衣服换了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也要收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了菜子  帮了我们大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是真是  有菜子在我们家就太平无事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了你刚才的那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句表扬还不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  要焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}啊啊  你们又在偷吃了  都跟你们说过不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}所以你们每次都是吃了几口就说已经饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子真的是个很认真的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是我靠表扬培育起来的啊  一定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  育儿的教育理论该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬王子殿下的人鱼公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许下愿望希望去看看地上的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海平面之上所见的王子殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是人鱼公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会憧憬王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海里随心畅游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是累了就稍作休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…陆地好可怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  对我来说  我的家一定是和海同在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  右脚鞋子找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我说过左边右边要好好放一处的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然照顾弟弟们很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但应该说这才是我的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  说你不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上不打工吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作…是要到下午的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}菜子  鞋子  鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  陆地上呼吸好困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近正好在开花季节的花是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说花吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不要那种羞答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拍一些成长与自然生机勃勃的花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生机…勃勃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边散步一边寻找这个季节的花儿也挺开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  为了明日的赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就早点睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在湖的前面有一片荞麦花丛生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个季节非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过斜坡陡得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿登山鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  为什么连这些我都没法立刻答上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没办法随心所欲地游
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  就稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  待会到办公室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家久等的工资哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少了一万五千元…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把鹤之间的花瓶弄坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因为被小孩子从后面撞了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那一撞…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你以后的工资里慢慢扣也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是九谷的高级货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要赔的话可远不止两三万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笔钱我万分感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比往常还要多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子深受期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到表扬之后为了与之相称
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们反而会自己做出努力以期改变的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这样如何呢  菜子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你把这笔钱交给我处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我正想写一些外汇投资小说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准唆使高中女生投资
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有那一万五千元的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄粉饼味的Tirol巧克力一块是二十元…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}（注：Tirol巧克力「チ ロルチョコ」，一种在日本深受女高中生和OL喜爱的小块巧克力）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二七十四  再是五…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七百五十个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  菜子能买好多个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  分给我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么分不分的  我又不会去买
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半…老板娘希望我改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她希望我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她希望我做出配得上这份工资的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你多半是那种被表扬后得意忘形的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我是褒义的  是褒义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是希望改变自己  才选择来打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是有这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里还算八面玲珑的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我觉得那应该才是真正的自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  难道说现在和我聊天的小菜不是真正的小菜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和绪花跟小民在一起的时候…稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的小菜快给我出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摸我额头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被人看见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摸额头啦～～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  拿工资啦～真好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过被扣了一万五千元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自由支配的收入基本上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  结名同学那个空了？给我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊  不过做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去灌自来水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这很催人泪下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买甘鲷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘鲷？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想挑战一次把它用于松风烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为是高级食材所以不让我摆弄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押水同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么特别的兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想学的东西也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会存起来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱还是舒舒服服用了才开心！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆跟我说过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱是可以磨砺人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨砺人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀！放学后去逛街吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逛街？好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是有闲钱去逛街的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给自己买一罐果汁如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我会买茶包泡大麦茶的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是看那些有点暴露的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民一直在挑那些三件一千元的打折T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦  斑点式样好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花的眼光很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是东京人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件泡泡袖真不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要试穿看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是没钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我做做梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是同一件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那类性感的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想变得性感啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得那么好的素材都没有被利用起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  押水同学再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进…进房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好成熟啊小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿…腿这里凉飕飕的…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  女孩果然会随衣装改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这套全部！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜真是大款
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于菜子的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这种状况下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有给她加薪水的余力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有立场说这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将盛开在这广阔的原野大片花朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押水同学  难得打扮上改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选曲品味却是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河灯祭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}把红色的缎带绑成花束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月下的法善寺小巷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月下的法善寺小巷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时总是吃弟弟们吃剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点决定不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然姜汁布丁很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十品蔬菜汉堡到底是用了什么蔬菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  尽量选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就吃小民吃剩下的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱我们平摊好了  放心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我最便宜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混合咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加点牛奶  尽可能多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长喝咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过喜欢奶咖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…又没那个钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太催人泪下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些我平时生活中不会遇到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  平时都在一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但像这样一起去什么地方玩是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来绪花也没什么朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就贬义上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是从褒义上来说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褒义上的没什么朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都心直口快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能树敌也很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是从褒义上来说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是觉得只要加上「从褒义上来说」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就什么都能被原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要口渴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比起水我更想要茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和可爱的女孩子们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新式的街头表演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝茶就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学  怎么能这样说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭讪啊  搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭讪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天想要光女生一起享受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在名为都市的沙漠里终于找到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…绿洲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜被搭讪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多蛋糕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  今天是过生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  给我草莓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这是怎么了  菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕也好  还有你这身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能是这样的改变  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且外观和工作一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也并不是那么想要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我自己也不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为都市的沙漠…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠的话就不能游泳了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么想游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更自由的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  甘鲷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃殿下在叫您哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人鱼也到了要追求时尚的时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这些好重啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力吧  成为能够配得上那些宝石的人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  太重要沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装饰品和期盼都太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要保持平常的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天马上就要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就下了血本打扮了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了15万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这刺绣夹克好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着这么搞笑的衣服来上班的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞…搞笑的打扮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不错…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  像和弟弟们在一起一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持平常的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fine fine fine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  需要我帮忙把行李拿进房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}fine  就这样  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}go go come
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}fine fine fine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常心  平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替您拿进房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急…慢慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便碰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在拍摄花开的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要从头来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之也已经得到谅解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不要再擅自乱来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是那种值得加薪的…那个…女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下这种错误
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘也许觉得我是个没用的女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可能在期待我的成长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我又不会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领悟能力又差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能好好接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可先说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你努力而加薪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种闲事我可从来没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们去学校的时候回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山上的花田  真是美丽得无法描述
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听女服务员的建议  买下的登山鞋真是正确
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还会再来见那位女服务员的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人认同了你的工作作风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才给你提高薪水的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作作风…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真正的我是更加开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音也是更加响亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许在喜翠庄的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹑手蹑脚  声音也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你却能注意到那些被人忽视的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且能够做出让人如沐春风的细致对应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这样的女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  鹤之间的客人说是吃不了青鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中自由泳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得菜子有点恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来黄粉饼和恶心小菜读音有点像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做了些有点对不起王子殿下的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我也要向着陆地出发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为此刻我觉得无论何处我都能随心畅游
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}一起来雪愿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}说的也是  文化祭  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}那个  其实我去工作也没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes  这是青春！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
